text: Mónika Király (born 10 November 1983) is a Hungarian road cyclist, who currently rides for UCI Women's Continental Team . She represented her nation at the 2004 and 2006 UCI Road World Championships. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Hungarian female cyclists Category:Living people Category:People from Mosonmagyaróvár Category:1983 births Category:Cyclists at the 2015 European Games Category:European Games competitors for Hungary
